<figure class="popup-accept">
    <div class="popup-accept__close">
        <svg class="icon" width="10" height="10">
            <use xlink:href="#close"></use>
        </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="popup-accept__title">
        Sure you want to accept?
    </div>
    <div class="popup-accept__text">
        Egestas arcu egestas parturient dui vitae. Ornare risus id ullamcorper in ut. Vestibulum neque ullamcorper non orci vel, consectetur mi, pulvinar. Eu lectus quis leo viverra lacus non fames est ut.
    </div>
    <div class="popup-accept__form">
        <form action="/" method="GET">
            <label for=""> Write your name </label>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Your Name">
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="popup-accept__cta">
        <button class="btn-bd"> No, Cancel </button>
        <button class="btn-main"> Yes, Confirm </button>
    </div>
</figure>

